# Built in Permissions
1. Admin - Can do anything, and also impersonate another user.
1. Edit project naming wizard
1. View project naming wizard
1. Full access to record/edit/publish videos
    1. May create new video project
    1. May record videos
    1. May edit videos
    1. May publish videos
1. May view reports at their level or below their level
    1. Level 3 users can view reports as levels 0 - 3
    2. This permits managers to see reports at different levels
